<div class="sections-page">
  <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-4">
    <div>
      <h1 class="page-heading size-md m-0"><i class="bi bi-magic me-2"></i><%= title %></h1>
      <div class="text-muted small mt-1">Active organization: <b><%= activeOrgName %></b> (<span class="font-monospace"><%= activeOrgId %></span>)</div>
    </div>
    <a href="<%= schoolSectionDashboardHref %>" class="school-navigator-dashboard btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <div class="form-container wide" style="max-width: 1400px;">
    <form id="sampleGeneratorForm" action="/school/sample-data" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="actionStateId" id="hid_actionStateId" value="<%= actionStateId || '' %>">

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <div class="alert alert-info border-info shadow-sm mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>
            This tool creates valid sample <b>Persons</b> and then registers them as <b>Students</b>, <b>Teachers</b>, or <b>Staff</b> in the current active organization.
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
              <label class="form-label fw-bold">Students</label>
              <input type="number" name="studentCount" class="form-control size-md" value="0" min="0" max="200">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
              <label class="form-label fw-bold">Teachers</label>
              <input type="number" name="teacherCount" class="form-control size-md" value="0" min="0" max="200">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
              <label class="form-label fw-bold">Staff</label>
              <input type="number" name="staffCount" class="form-control size-md" value="0" min="0" max="200">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
              <label class="form-label fw-bold">Name Prefix</label>
              <input type="text" name="prefix" class="form-control size-md" value="Sample" maxlength="30" placeholder="Sample">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-check mb-3">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="createLinkedAccounts" id="createLinkedAccounts" checked>
            <label class="form-check-label fw-bold" for="createLinkedAccounts">
              Create linked school accounts when matching head accounts are available
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="small text-muted">
            Limits: max <b>200</b> items for each group in one run.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <div class="alert alert-warning border-warning shadow-sm mb-4">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
            This action clears <b>Academic Ledger</b>, <b>Transaction Book</b>, <b>Journals</b>, <b>Program/Term Registrations</b>, <b>Prior Subject Credits</b>, <b>Withdrawals</b>, <b>Class Enrollments</b> (including enrollment period rows and completion-decision fields), per-class folders under <code>classes_storage</code> <em>and</em> embedded <code>sessions</code> on class rows in <code>classes.json</code> (JSON) or <code>schoolClasses</code> (Mongo), <b>Report Instances &amp; Assignments</b> (templates stay), <b>Timesheets</b> (period definitions stay), per-subject folders under <code>subjects_storage</code>, <b>Attendance Matrix Policy</b> overrides for this org (JSON or Mongo), <b>Official Final Grades</b> workflow state on classes in this org, and optional migration log files. It then rebuilds teacher/student schedule indexes for classes in this org. Master row definitions remain (accounts, people, programs, terms, classes, subjects, report templates, timesheet periods).
          </div>

          <div class="form-check mb-3">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="includeAcademicSnapshots" checked>
            <label class="form-check-label fw-bold" for="includeAcademicSnapshots">
              Also clear academic snapshots (recommended for clean test runs)
            </label>
          </div>

          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-md fw-bold px-4" id="btnClearTransactionalData">
            Clear Transactions, Registrations & Withdrawals
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <div class="alert alert-danger border-danger shadow-sm mb-3">
            <i class="bi bi-trash3-fill me-2"></i>
            <b>Destructive sample cleanup:</b> review and permanently delete sample <b>Students</b>, <b>Teachers</b>, <b>Staff</b>, selected associated <b>Persons</b>, and eligible linked school accounts.
          </div>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-md fw-bold px-4" id="btnOpenSamplePeopleDeleteModal">
            Delete Sample People (Selectable)
          </button>
          <div class="small text-muted mt-2">
            Recommended order: first run transactional clear, then run this people cleanup for a fully clean school workspace.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="button-row mt-4 pt-3 border-top">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-filled btn-primary btn-md fw-bold px-4" id="btnGenerateSamples">Generate Sample Data</button>
        <a href="<%= schoolSectionDashboardHref %>" class="school-navigator-dashboard btn btn-filled btn-secondary btn-md">Cancel</a>
      </div>
    </form>

    <div id="sampleGeneratorResult" class="mt-4"></div>
    <div id="samplePeopleDeleteResult" class="mt-4"></div>
    <div id="sampleResetResult" class="mt-4"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="sampleDataOperationModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="sampleDataOperationModalLabel" aria-hidden="true" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content border-0 shadow">
      <div class="modal-body p-4">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="spinner-border text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" role="status" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1" id="sampleDataOperationModalLabel">Working on your request</h5>
            <div class="text-muted small" id="sampleDataOperationSubtitle">Please keep this page open.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress mb-3" style="height: 16px;" role="progressbar" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" aria-valuenow="0">
          <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" id="sampleDataOperationProgressBar" style="width: 0%;">0%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="small fw-semibold" id="sampleDataOperationComment">Preparing...</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="samplePeopleDeleteModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="samplePeopleDeleteModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-scrollable">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="samplePeopleDeleteModalLabel">
          <i class="bi bi-trash3 me-2"></i>Delete Sample People (Selectable)
        </h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="alert alert-warning border-warning mb-3">
          <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
          This cleanup is permanent. Only sample-marked records from the active organization are listed.
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 align-items-center mb-3">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" id="btnSelectAllSamplePeople">Select All</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" id="btnUnselectAllSamplePeople">Unselect All</button>
          <span class="small text-muted ms-2" id="samplePeopleSelectionSummaryText"></span>
        </div>
        <div id="samplePeopleDeleteModalContent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <div class="small text-muted" id="samplePeopleDeleteImpactText"></div>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" id="btnConfirmSamplePeopleDelete">
            Delete Selected
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<% if (lastResult) { %>
<script>
  window.__LAST_SAMPLE_GENERATOR_RESULT__ = <%- JSON.stringify(lastResult).replace(/</g, '\\u003c') %>;
</script>
<% } else { %>
<script>window.__LAST_SAMPLE_GENERATOR_RESULT__ = null;</script>
<% } %>
<% if (lastResetResult) { %>
<script>
  window.__LAST_SAMPLE_RESET_RESULT__ = <%- JSON.stringify(lastResetResult).replace(/</g, '\\u003c') %>;
</script>
<% } else { %>
<script>window.__LAST_SAMPLE_RESET_RESULT__ = null;</script>
<% } %>

<script>
(function () {
  const form = document.getElementById('sampleGeneratorForm');
  const resultEl = document.getElementById('sampleGeneratorResult');
  const peopleDeleteResultEl = document.getElementById('samplePeopleDeleteResult');
  const resetResultEl = document.getElementById('sampleResetResult');
  const submitBtn = document.getElementById('btnGenerateSamples');
  const clearBtn = document.getElementById('btnClearTransactionalData');
  const openPeopleDeleteBtn = document.getElementById('btnOpenSamplePeopleDeleteModal');
  const selectAllPeopleBtn = document.getElementById('btnSelectAllSamplePeople');
  const unselectAllPeopleBtn = document.getElementById('btnUnselectAllSamplePeople');
  const confirmPeopleDeleteBtn = document.getElementById('btnConfirmSamplePeopleDelete');
  const peopleDeleteModalEl = document.getElementById('samplePeopleDeleteModal');
  const peopleDeleteModalContentEl = document.getElementById('samplePeopleDeleteModalContent');
  const peopleDeleteSelectionSummaryTextEl = document.getElementById('samplePeopleSelectionSummaryText');
  const peopleDeleteImpactTextEl = document.getElementById('samplePeopleDeleteImpactText');
  const includeSnapshotsCheckbox = document.getElementById('includeAcademicSnapshots');
  const actionStateInput = document.getElementById('hid_actionStateId');
  const operationModalEl = document.getElementById('sampleDataOperationModal');
  const operationTitleEl = document.getElementById('sampleDataOperationModalLabel');
  const operationSubtitleEl = document.getElementById('sampleDataOperationSubtitle');
  const operationCommentEl = document.getElementById('sampleDataOperationComment');
  const operationProgressBarEl = document.getElementById('sampleDataOperationProgressBar');
  const operationProgressWrapEl = operationProgressBarEl ? operationProgressBarEl.closest('.progress') : null;

  let samplePeoplePreview = null;
  let peopleDeleteModalApi = null;
  let operationModalApi = null;
  let operationProgressTimer = null;
  let operationStageTimer = null;
  let operationProgressValue = 0;
  let operationStageIndex = 0;
  let operationStages = [];
  let peopleDeleteSubmissionActive = false;

  function showMsg(opts) {
    if (typeof showMessageModal === 'function') return showMessageModal(opts);
    alert(opts?.message || 'Done');
    return Promise.resolve();
  }

  function getOperationModalApi() {
    if (operationModalApi) return operationModalApi;
    if (operationModalEl && window.bootstrap && window.bootstrap.Modal) {
      operationModalApi = window.bootstrap.Modal.getOrCreateInstance(operationModalEl, {
        backdrop: 'static',
        keyboard: false
      });
      return operationModalApi;
    }
    return null;
  }

  function setOperationProgress(value, comment) {
    const nextValue = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, Math.round(Number(value || 0))));
    operationProgressValue = nextValue;
    if (operationProgressBarEl) {
      operationProgressBarEl.style.width = `${nextValue}%`;
      operationProgressBarEl.textContent = `${nextValue}%`;
    }
    if (operationProgressWrapEl) {
      operationProgressWrapEl.setAttribute('aria-valuenow', String(nextValue));
    }
    if (operationCommentEl && comment) {
      operationCommentEl.textContent = comment;
    }
  }

  function stopOperationTimers() {
    if (operationProgressTimer) {
      window.clearInterval(operationProgressTimer);
      operationProgressTimer = null;
    }
    if (operationStageTimer) {
      window.clearInterval(operationStageTimer);
      operationStageTimer = null;
    }
  }

  function showOperationModal(config) {
    stopOperationTimers();
    operationProgressValue = 8;
    operationStageIndex = 0;
    operationStages = Array.isArray(config?.stages) && config.stages.length
      ? config.stages
      : ['Preparing request...', 'Processing records...', 'Finalizing result...'];

    if (operationTitleEl) operationTitleEl.textContent = String(config?.title || 'Working on your request');
    if (operationSubtitleEl) operationSubtitleEl.textContent = String(config?.subtitle || 'Please keep this page open.');
    setOperationProgress(operationProgressValue, operationStages[0]);

    const api = getOperationModalApi();
    if (api) {
      api.show();
    } else if (operationModalEl) {
      operationModalEl.style.display = 'block';
      operationModalEl.classList.add('show');
      operationModalEl.removeAttribute('aria-hidden');
      operationModalEl.setAttribute('aria-modal', 'true');
      operationModalEl.setAttribute('role', 'dialog');
      document.body.classList.add('modal-open');
    }

    operationProgressTimer = window.setInterval(() => {
      const cap = operationProgressValue < 55 ? 72 : 92;
      if (operationProgressValue >= cap) return;
      const step = operationProgressValue < 45 ? 4 : 2;
      setOperationProgress(Math.min(cap, operationProgressValue + step));
    }, 900);

    operationStageTimer = window.setInterval(() => {
      if (!operationStages.length) return;
      operationStageIndex = Math.min(operationStages.length - 1, operationStageIndex + 1);
      if (operationCommentEl) operationCommentEl.textContent = operationStages[operationStageIndex];
    }, 2600);
  }

  async function completeOperationModal(comment) {
    stopOperationTimers();
    setOperationProgress(100, comment || 'Completed. Preparing result...');
    await new Promise((resolve) => window.setTimeout(resolve, 350));
    hideOperationModal();
  }

  function hideOperationModal() {
    stopOperationTimers();
    const api = getOperationModalApi();
    if (api) {
      api.hide();
      return;
    }
    if (!operationModalEl) return;
    operationModalEl.classList.remove('show');
    operationModalEl.style.display = 'none';
    operationModalEl.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
    operationModalEl.removeAttribute('aria-modal');
    document.body.classList.remove('modal-open');
  }

  function isAdminVerificationCancel(error) {
    return error && error.code === 'ADMIN_VERIFICATION_CANCELLED';
  }

  function isAdminRequiredError(error) {
    return error && error.code === 'ADMIN_VERIFICATION_REQUIRED';
  }

  async function ensureAdminVerification() {
    if (typeof window.requestProtectedAction !== 'function') {
      throw new Error('Admin verification system is not loaded. Please refresh the page and try again.');
    }
    await window.requestProtectedAction();
  }

  async function readJsonResponse(response, fallbackMessage) {
    const result = await response.json().catch(() => ({}));
    if (response.status === 403 && result?.status === 'admin_required') {
      if (typeof window.resetAdminVerificationCache === 'function') {
        window.resetAdminVerificationCache();
      }
      const error = new Error(result.message || fallbackMessage || 'Admin approval required or session expired.');
      error.code = 'ADMIN_VERIFICATION_REQUIRED';
      throw error;
    }
    return result;
  }

  function safeHtml(value) {
    return String(value || '')
      .replace(/&/g, '&amp;')
      .replace(/</g, '&lt;')
      .replace(/>/g, '&gt;')
      .replace(/"/g, '&quot;')
      .replace(/'/g, '&#39;');
  }

  function getPeopleDeleteModalApi() {
    if (peopleDeleteModalApi) return peopleDeleteModalApi;
    if (peopleDeleteModalEl && window.bootstrap && window.bootstrap.Modal) {
      peopleDeleteModalApi = window.bootstrap.Modal.getOrCreateInstance(peopleDeleteModalEl);
      return peopleDeleteModalApi;
    }
    return null;
  }

  function showPeopleDeleteModal() {
    const api = getPeopleDeleteModalApi();
    if (api) {
      api.show();
      return;
    }
    if (!peopleDeleteModalEl) return;
    peopleDeleteModalEl.style.display = 'block';
    peopleDeleteModalEl.classList.add('show');
    peopleDeleteModalEl.removeAttribute('aria-hidden');
    peopleDeleteModalEl.setAttribute('aria-modal', 'true');
    peopleDeleteModalEl.setAttribute('role', 'dialog');
    document.body.classList.add('modal-open');
  }

  function hidePeopleDeleteModal() {
    const api = getPeopleDeleteModalApi();
    if (api) {
      api.hide();
      return;
    }
    if (!peopleDeleteModalEl) return;
    peopleDeleteModalEl.classList.remove('show');
    peopleDeleteModalEl.style.display = 'none';
    peopleDeleteModalEl.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
    peopleDeleteModalEl.removeAttribute('aria-modal');
    document.body.classList.remove('modal-open');
  }

  function renderResult(payload) {
    if (!payload || !payload.summary) {
      resultEl.innerHTML = '';
      return;
    }

    const summary = payload.summary || {};
    const warnings = Array.isArray(payload.warnings) ? payload.warnings : [];
    const errors = Array.isArray(payload.errors) ? payload.errors : [];

    resultEl.innerHTML = `
      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header bg-white py-3">
          <h5 class="m-0 fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-list-check me-2"></i>Generation Result</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <div class="row g-3 mb-3">
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Students Created</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-primary">${Number(summary.created?.students || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Teachers Created</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-success">${Number(summary.created?.teachers || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Staff Created</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-warning">${Number(summary.created?.staff || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Failures</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(summary.failed || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          ${warnings.length ? `
            <div class="alert alert-warning border-warning">
              <div class="fw-bold mb-2">Warnings</div>
              <ul class="mb-0">
                ${warnings.map(item => `<li>${safeHtml(item)}</li>`).join('')}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ` : ''}

          ${errors.length ? `
            <div class="alert alert-danger border-danger mb-0">
              <div class="fw-bold mb-2">Errors</div>
              <ul class="mb-0">
                ${errors.map(item => `<li>${safeHtml(item)}</li>`).join('')}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ` : ''}
        </div>
      </div>
    `;
  }

  function renderResetResult(payload) {
    if (!payload || !payload.summary) {
      resetResultEl.innerHTML = '';
      return;
    }
    const cleared = payload.summary.cleared || {};
    const remaining = payload.summary.remaining || {};
    const resetWarnings = Array.isArray(payload.warnings) ? payload.warnings : [];

    resetResultEl.innerHTML = `
      <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-header bg-white py-3">
          <h5 class="m-0 fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-eraser me-2"></i>Transactional Reset Result</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          ${resetWarnings.length ? `
            <div class="alert alert-warning border-warning mb-3">
              <div class="fw-bold mb-2">Warnings</div>
              <ul class="mb-0 small">
                ${resetWarnings.map(item => `<li>${safeHtml(item)}</li>`).join('')}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ` : ''}
          <div class="row g-3 mb-3">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Academic Ledger Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.academicLedgerEntries || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Global Transactions Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.globalTransactions || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Journals Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.transactionJournals || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Program Reg. Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.programRegistrations || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Prior Subject Credits Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.priorSubjectCredits || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Term Reg. Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.termRegistrations || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Enroll. Periods Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.classEnrollmentPeriods || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Withdrawals Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.withdrawals || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Legacy Class Roster Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.classEnrollments || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Snapshots Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.academicSnapshots || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Report Instances Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.reportInstances || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Report Assignments Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.reportAssignments || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Timesheets Cleared</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.timesheets || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Class Workspaces Removed</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.classRuntimeDirs || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Embedded sessions cleared (class rows)</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.embeddedSessionsClearedClasses || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
              <div class="border rounded-3 p-3 h-100">
                <div class="small text-muted">Subject Storage Dirs Removed</div>
                <div class="fs-4 fw-bold text-danger">${Number(cleared.subjectStorageDirs || 0)}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4">
